			      TestGroups
			      ==========

This file list all test groups with a short description that are
currently present in the Octopus testsuite. This is intended as a
reference to avoid a jungle of groups.


Group tag       Description
------------------------------------------------------------------------
short-run       Formerly known as -s flag. Run by 'make check'.
long-run        Should include everything not in 'short-run'.

components             Each below is for the corresponding directory.
finite_systems_1d
finite_systems_2d
finite_systems_3d
functionals
linear_response
open_systems
optimal_control
periodic_systems
photo_electron
real_time
